text: Austin Davis (born October 4, 1989) is an American Democratic politician who is the 35th Lieutenant Governor of Pennsylvania since 2023. He was a member of the Pennsylvania House of Representatives, representing the 35th District from 2018 to 2022. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Pennsylvania General Assembly Category:Lieutenant Governors of Pennsylvania Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:African-American politicians
